In terms of applications, hospitals are the primary contributors to the market share, owing to their advanced medical facilities and the preference of COVID-19 patients for seeking treatment in hospital settings. Clinics are also embracing traditional Chinese medicine for COVID-19 treatment, reflecting a shift towards integrative healthcare practices. The distribution channels for TCM products include retail pharmacies and online pharmacies, with the latter gaining traction due to the convenience and accessibility offered by e-commerce platforms. Retail pharmacies remain crucial for the availability of over-the-counter traditional Chinese medicine products, ensuring widespread access to these remedies.

